		<summary>The free PDF24 PDF Creator is a program to create PDF files from almost any application. The PDF software is a free PDF creator to create PDF files from any type of document. With the PDF creator you can convert documents into PDF files very easily. The PDF creator acts as a PDF printer.</summary>
		<description>The free PDF24 PDF Creator is a program to create PDF files from almost any application. The PDF software is a free PDF creator to create PDF files from any type of document. With the PDF creator you can convert documents into PDF files very easily. The PDF creator acts as a PDF printer. 

__General__
- Create a PDF file out of any application which provides a print option.
- Creation of other file types: PDF/A, PDF/X, PS, EPS, PCL, PNG, JPEG, BMP, PCX, TIFF, PSD
- Self-explanatory user interfaces
- Easy installation with a few clicks
- PDF creation assistant, PDF editor, PDF screen capture
- New PDF printer driver with more features
- Profiles to control quality and size of a PDF
- Find out a PDF file name from the Windows printing interface for PDF files generated by PDF printer
- Convert images to PDF
- PDF watermark and PDF stamp
- Supports digital paper, letter paper
- Secure a PDF with a password
- Set document properties and permissions
- Sign PDF files
- Personalize PDF24 Creator
- Automated updates
- Supported multi-user environments
- New settings area with a lot of new options
- Windows tray icon with useful features
- For all Windows versions from Windows XP upwards
__PDF24 Assistant__
- Contains often-used functions for creating PDF files (save PDF, show PDF, edit PDF, send PDF via email)
- Can be personalized with own logo (see [www.pdf24.org](www.pdf24.org) )
- Easy profile assignment to a created PDF
- Preview to have a fast overview of a created PDF.
__PDF24 Editor__
- Automatic conversion of documents (Word, Excel, images, and more) to PDF
- Convert documents such as Word, Excel, and images to PDF automatically
- Integrated file explorer for choosing documents
- Varying preview modes to edit PDF documents easily
- Integrated PDF viewer
- Merge multiple PDF documents into one
- Split PDF documents, extract pages from one document and create new PDF files
- Send created PDF files via email
- Extract text from a PDF file.
- Print a created PDF file
__PDF24 Screen Capture__
- Create PDF files from screen content
- Creates PDF files from whole screen, screen working area, active window, active window content, from a user defined screen area and from Windows clipboard.
__Supports TWAIN interface.__
- Can import images from devices like scanners, digicams and webcams if they support TWAIN.
- Enables you to create PDF image maps based on images in a digicam
__PDF24 Windows Tray Icon__
- Contains the PDF screen capture feature
- Contains some other useful features

[Changelog](https://en.pdf24.org/pdf-creator-changelog.html)
